<h2 id="2-dicion√°rio-texmaker">2. DICION√ÅRIO TEXMAKER</h2>
<p>Instale o pacote myspell-pt-br:</p>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>myspell-pt-br
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>No Texmaker, acesse <strong>Options -&gt; Configure Texmaker</strong>, e na aba Editor selecione o dicion√°rio pt_BR.dic que se encontra no diret√≥rio <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/usr/share/hunspell</code>
Para os caracteres, lembrar de usar: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ISO-8859-15</code>.</p>

<h2 id="3-lyx">3. LYX</h2>
