<h2 id="16-instalar-adobe-flash-player">16. INSTALAR ADOBE FLASH PLAYER</h2>

<p>I am using this few steps:</p>

<p>Download flash player <strong>.tar.gz</strong></p>

<p>Extract it and you can see usr and <strong>libflashplayer.so</strong></p>

<p>Now open terminal and use this command (in folder where you have extracted usr and libflash‚Ä¶) for copy usr folder:</p>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo cp</span> <span class="nt">-r</span> usr/<span class="k">*</span> /usr
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Copy <strong>libflashplayer.so to</strong> <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/usr/lib/firefox-addons/plugins</code> with this command (in folder where you have extracted usr and libflash‚Ä¶)</p>

<p><strong>For Firefox:</strong></p>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo cp </span>libflashplayer.so /usr/lib/firefox-addons/plugins
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><strong>For Chromium:</strong></p>
<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo cp </span>libflashplayer.so /usr/lib/chromium-browser/pepper/
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Para ver: chrome://plugins</p>

