<h1 id="outros-comandos">OUTROS COMANDOS</h1>
<ol>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo su</code> (entra como root)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo chmod +x ./install</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo nautilus</code>  (d√° acesso total)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo dpkg -i Downloads/nomedoarquivo</code>  (instalar pacote .deb)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">tar -zxvf nome_do_pacote.tar.gz</code>  (descompacta arquivo tar.gz)</p>
  </li>
  <li>Para encontrar um frase (ou express√£o) em arquivos dentro de uma pasta, entre na pasta desejada:
    <blockquote>
      <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">cd</span> /home/<span class="nv">$USER</span>/folder
</code></pre></div>      </div>
      <p>e aqui digite o comando abaixo:</p>
      <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  find ./<span class="k">*</span> <span class="nt">-type</span> f <span class="nt">-exec</span> <span class="nb">grep</span> <span class="nt">-l</span> palavra-ou-expressao-a-pesquisar <span class="o">{}</span> <span class="se">\;</span>
</code></pre></div>      </div>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">evince [nomedoarquivo.x]</code>  (visualizador de arquivos)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ grep -rin "STRING" ./*</code>   (Localiza a ‚Äústring‚Äù na pasta local)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Reinicia o computador: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">shutdown -r now</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Desliga o computador: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">shutdown -h now</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>Permiss√£o de um arquivo:
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">chmod </span>751 &lt;nome da pasta ou arquivo.extens√£o&gt;
</code></pre></div>    </div>
    <p>0 = Nenhuma permiss√£o<br />
1 = Apenas execu√ß√£o<br />
2 = Apenas grava√ß√£o<br />
3 = Execu√ß√£o e grava√ß√£o<br />
4 = Apenas leitura<br />
5 = Execu√ß√£o e leitura<br />
6 = Leitura e grava√ß√£o<br />
7 = Todos; leitura, grava√ß√£o e execu√ß√£o</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<blockquote>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Permission</th>
        <th>rwx</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>7 full</td>
        <td>111</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>6 read and write</td>
        <td>110</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>5 read and execute</td>
        <td>101</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>4 read only</td>
        <td>100</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>3 write and execute</td>
        <td>011</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>2 write only</td>
        <td>010</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>1 execute only</td>
        <td>001</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>0 none</td>
        <td>000</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</blockquote>

