</code></pre></div>    </div>
    <p>procure pela linha <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#force_color_prompt=yes</code> e tire o s√≠mbolo <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#</code>. Lembre de atualizar: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$ source .bashrc</code>.</p>
  </li>
