<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">sudo </span>mount <span class="nt">-t</span> vboxsf nome_pasta_compartilhada /mnt/nome_pasta
