</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>If you want to check the available formats:
    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>youtube-dl <span class="nt">-F</span> http://www.youtube.com/watch?v<span class="o">=</span>wUln3JuE7iU
